, you probably see them every day, but have you ever properly met a pigeon? Now's your chance! We are happy to invite ambassador pigeons and human members of Palomacy , a volunteer, nonprofit rescue dedicated to saving the lives of domestic (unreleasable) pigeons and doves to our Saturday morning story time. We will hear stories, songs, and more and have time to meet and learn about pigeons. There will also be a craft for the whole family.  Maybe pigeons can't drive buses, but they are beautiful, friendly, and full of surprises!","activity_type":["indoor","educational"],"age_buckets":["0-2","3-5","6-8","9-12","13+"],"min_price":0,"max_price":0,"location_address":"2090 Kittredge Street, Berkeley, CA 94704","location_lat":null,"location_lon":null,"location_environment":"indoor","accessibility_wheelchair":true,"accessibility_stroller":true,"facilities_restrooms":true,"facilities_changingtable":null,"schedule_openinghours":null,"duration_minutes":30,"imageurlthumb":"https://berkeleypubliclibrary.libnet.info/images/events/berkeleypubliclibrary/Palomacy.png","urlmoreinfo":"https://berkeleypubliclibrary.libnet.info/event/16309173","trail_lengthkm":null,"trail_durationminutes":null,"trail_routetype":null,"event_starttime":"2026-05-23 10:30:00","event_endtime":"2026-05-23 11:00:00","ticket_url":"https://berkeleypubliclibrary.libnet.info/event/16309173","organizer":"berkeley_public_library","foodvenue_kidmenu":null,"foodvenue_kidcorner":null,"foodvenue_kidamenities":null,"schema_version":"v3.2-scrape","source":"berkeley_public_library","json":{"id":"scrape-berkeley_public_library-16309173","name":"Family Story Time with Special Guests--Pigeons!","description":"Pigeons are fascinating creatures, you probably see them every day, but have you ever properly met a pigeon? Now's your chance! We are happy to invite ambassador pigeons and human members of Palomacy , a volunteer, nonprofit rescue dedicated to saving the lives of domestic (unreleasable) pigeons and doves to our Saturda